text: Hendrik Rasmussen (4 April 1887 - 5 August 1969) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
